# Secret used to sign the session cookie AND encrypt stored service tokens at
# rest (Plex/Tautulli/Seerr/*arr).
#
# OPTIONAL in Docker: leave unset and the container generates one on first
# boot, persisted at /data/.session-secret (recommended — it then lives with
# the database it protects and survives recreates automatically).
#
# Set it only to manage the secret yourself. Generate with: openssl rand -hex 32
# NOTE: changing an in-use secret invalidates sessions and stored tokens.
# SESSION_SECRET=

# Optional: where the SQLite db lives. Defaults to ./data locally, /data in Docker.
# DATA_DIR=/data

# Optional: public URL of this app (used to build the Plex auth forwardUrl).
# If empty, the browser origin is used.
# APP_URL=https://keeparr.example.net
